Monsters, Inc.;;90;;96;;G;;Monsters Incorporated is the largest scare factory in the monster world, and James P. Sullivan (John Goodman) is one of its top scarers. Sullivan is a huge, intimidating monster with blue fur, large purple spots and horns. His scare assistant, best friend and roommate is Mike Wazowski (Billy Crystal), a green, opinionated, feisty little one-eyed monster. Visiting from the human world is Boo (Mary Gibbs), a tiny girl who goes where no human has ever gone before.;;Fantasy,Animation,Comedy,Adventure,Kids & family;;Pete Docter;;2001;;John Goodman,Billy Crystal,Mary Gibbs,Steve Buscemi,James Coburn,Jennifer Tilly,Bob Peterson,John Ratzenberger,Frank Oz,Steve Susskind,Bonnie Hunt,Jeff Pidgeon,Sam Black;;https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/monsters_inc